  "title": "Account Assistant",
  "description": "<h2>Accountant</h2><h2>Account Executive</h2><h2>Account Assistant</h2><h2>Account Clerk</h2><p><strong>Location:</strong> West Coast / Clementi, Singapore</p><h3>Job Description</h3><p>The Accountant will be responsible for handling the full spectrum of accounting functions for the clinic, ensuring accurate financial records, timely reporting, and compliance with Singapore accounting and tax requirements.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Handle <strong>full set of accounts</strong> (AP, AR, GL, bank reconciliations)</p></li><li><p>Prepare monthly financial statements and management reports</p></li><li><p>Manage <strong>GST submissions and claims</strong></p></li><li><p>Handle <strong>tax filing</strong>, including corporate tax computations and liaison with tax agents/auditors</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate accounting records using <strong>Xero accounting software</strong></p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with Singapore accounting standards and statutory requirements</p></li><li><p>Support budgeting, cash flow monitoring, and financial planning</p></li><li><p>Perform other ad-hoc accounting and administrative duties as required</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Diploma / Degree in Accounting, Finance, or a related field</p></li><li><p><strong>Proven experience in full set accounting</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Hands-on experience with Xero accounting software</strong> (mandatory)</p></li><li><p>Familiar with <strong>GST regulations and tax filing in Singapore</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong attention to detail and good organizational skills</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and meet deadlines</p></li><li><p>Experience in SME or healthcare/veterinary industry is an advantage</p></li></ul><h3>Employment Type</h3><ul><li><p>Full-time / Part-time (to be discussed)</p></li></ul><p>Interested candidates, please send your resume with expected salary and availability to:</p><p><strong>Email:</strong> OmniVet.hr@gmail.com</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>",
